IRectangleRenderer<N,java.awt.Graphics2D,java.awt.Color>
public class DefaultRectangleRenderer<N>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRectangleRenderer<N,java.awt.Graphics2D,java.awt.Color>

The default rectangle renderer simply renders the given rectangle using the color provided by the color provider. The rectangle is framed white when it is highlighted. The renderer does not paint any labels.
